      • getContainingEntityClass

        public Class<? extends DeviceEntity> getContainingEntityClass(String oidValue)
        Description copied from interface: IClassRegistry
        Deliver the class of the database entity that contains an element with a specified oid value
        Specified by:
        getContainingEntityClass in interface IClassRegistry
        Parameters:
        oidValue - the value of the OID to be checked
        Returns:
        the class which contains a field with the specified oid. If oidValue refers to a table entry, the class of the parent table will be returned. If oidValue refers to a scalar, the class of the parent entity will be returned. Otherwise, the entity associated with the specified oid is returned.
